window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Tatum Kelly's life was spiraling.</b></p> <p>The funding for the women's hockey team was cut, her scholarship was ruined, and her hopes for the season were gone. With nothing else to lose, Tatum joins the men's team, much to the dismay of captain Callum O'Neil. Luckily for them, you don't need to be friends to be winners.</p> <p>As the tension builds, Callum's best friends, Jace and Shawn, pursue Tatum's respect, both on and off the ice. Determined to make this season her best yet, Tatum knows better than to get involved with one teammate, much less two. But what if hockey isn't enough for her anymore? What if she finds her missing piece... or pieces?</p> <p><i>Contains mature content.</i></p>"; 
